behind%20the%20plant%20in%20the%20image%20above.)%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Frame%20comes%20with%20a%20wired%20One%20Connect%20Box%2C%20which%20simplifies%20power%20and%20device%20connections%20through%20a%20single%20cable%20that%20runs%20from%20the%20screen%20to%20the%20box.%20Thanks%20to%20this%20design%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20move%20the%20TV%20if%20I%20want%20to%20connect%20an%20antenna%20to%20it%20or%20add%20a%20new%20game%20console%2C%20as%20I%20can%20just%20plug%20components%20into%20the%20box%20and%20keep%20the%20box%20out%20of%20sight.%20The%20wired%20cable%20is%20thin%20and%20transparent%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20navigate%20fireplaces%20and%20other%20structural%20inconveniences.%20I%20keep%20mine%20hidden%20by%20a%20plant%20on%20my%20media%20console.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung's%20Art%20Store%20is%20packed%20with%20high-quality%20images%20that%20can%20be%20displayed%20on%20the%20Frame%20TV.%20The%20selection%20is%20much%20more%20comprehensive%20than%20the%20free%20offerings%20provided%20by%20Hisense%20and%20TCL.%20But%20while%20Samsung%20does%20offer%20a%20limited%20stream%20of%20free%20curated%20artwork%2C%20to%20get%20access%20to%20the%20whole%20collection%2C%20you%20need%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20paid%20subscription.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV's%20anti-glare%2C%20matte%20screen%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20keeping%20it%20visible%20in%20sun-filled%20rooms%20%E2%80%94%20both%20in%20art%20mode%20and%20when%20watching%20content%20during%20the%20day.%20But%20like%20most%20art%20TVs%2C%20the%20Frame's%20image%20quality%20is%20nothing%20special.%20Brightness%20is%20limited%20to%20about%20500%20nits%2C%20and%20contrast%20is%20relatively%20low%20compared%20to%20a%20typical%20midrange%20TV%20meant%20for%20home%20theaters.%20The%20TV's%20edge-lit%20backlighting%20is%20often%20visible%20across%20scenes%20in%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%2C%20causing%20elevated%20black%20levels.%20In%20the%20dark%2C%20this%20uneven%20lighting%20can%20be%20downright%20distracting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20Frame%20isn't%20built%20for%20picture%20quality%20aficionados.%20It's%20built%20for%20design-focused%20buyers%20who%20want%20a%20TV%20that%20doubles%20as%20a%20piece%20of%20art%20in%20their%20living%20room.%20And%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20it%20excels.%20I%20also%20love%20that%20it's%20available%20in%20several%20screen%20sizes.%20The%20latest%202025%20model%20ranges%20from%2043%20to%2065%20inches%2C%20but%20you%20can%20still%20find%20older%20versions%20of%20the%20TV%20in%20sizes%20ranging%20from%2032%20to%2085%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-samsung-tvs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20Samsung%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22229e26ad-61f8-4379-bbb4-c7c1ff23a5ff%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20high-end%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20high-end%20model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Frame%20Pro%20is%20Samsung's%20new%20high-end%20art-style%20TV.%20It's%20the%20most%20advanced%20option%20on%20the%20market%20and%20offers%20a%20noticeably%20bolder%2C%20brighter%20image%20than%20any%20other%20display%20in%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20model%20carries%20over%20all%20of%20the%20essential%20features%20found%20on%20the%20standard%20Frame%20TV%2C%20including%20a%20matte%20screen%2C%20support%20for%20attachable%20bezels%2C%20a%20flush%20wall%20mount%2C%20and%20a%20motion%20sensor.%20What%20sets%20this%20model%20apart%20from%20Samsung's%20cheaper%20Frame%20is%20its%20wireless%20connection%20box%20and%20local%20dimming%20backlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20standard%20Frame%20TV%2C%20the%20Frame%20Pro%20uses%20a%20separate%20One%20Connect%20Box%20to%20house%20its%20video%20ports.%20But%20the%20Frame%20Pro%20goes%20one%20step%20further%20by%20making%20this