0(HDR)%20videos%20and%20helps%20it%20overcome%20ambient%20light%20in%20rooms%20with%20many%20windows.%20The%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20can%20also%20produce%20deeper%20black%20levels%20than%20other%20art%20frame%20TVs%2C%20so%20dark%20scenes%20don't%20look%20as%20washed%20out%20and%20uneven%20when%20watching%20TV%20with%20the%20lights%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20there%20are%20still%20some%20caveats%20that%20prevent%20the%20Frame%20Pro%20from%20being%20a%20complete%20slam%20dunk%20for%20everyone.%20The%20biggest%20consideration%2C%20quite%20literally%2C%20is%20its%20size.%20The%20Frame%20Pro%20is%20only%20offered%20in%2065-%2C%2075-%2C%20and%2085-inch%20options.%20Those%20large%20sizes%20won't%20work%20for%20everyone.%20Additionally%2C%20though%20the%20Frame%20Pro's%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20is%20an%20improvement%20over%20a%20regular%20LED%20panel%2C%20I%20still%20noticed%20some%20light%20blotches%20and%20uneven%20dimming%20during%20some%20dark%20scenes%20in%20nighttime%20viewing.%20So%20while%20this%20is%20the%20best%20frame%20TV%20for%20picture%20quality%2C%20it%20still%20can't%20match%20the%20image%20performance%20of%20most%20traditional%20midrange%20QLED%20and%20OLED%20TVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20it's%20also%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20access%20to%20Samsung's%20full%20Art%20Store%20requires%20a%20subscription%20fee%2C%20and%20that%20magnetic%20bezel%20attachments%20cost%20extra.%20But%20while%20this%20all%20adds%20to%20the%20price%2C%20the%20Frame%20Pro%20is%20easily%20the%20best%20art%20TV%20for%20premium%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-frame-pro-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESamsung%20Frame%20Pro%20TV%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233391db5-43b2-4a38-9867-1a47d5ef82ef%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20Frame%20TV%20alternative%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20Frame%20TV%20alternative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hisense%20CanvasTV%20is%20a%20strong%20Frame%20TV%20competitor%2C%20and%20does%20a%20solid%20job%20of%20matching%20most%20of%20the%20standard%20Samsung%20Frame's%20features%20and%20design%20perks.%20It%20has%20all%20the%20essentials%20that%20make%20an%20art%20TV%20an%20art%20TV%2C%20including%20a%20matte%20screen%2C%20support%20for%20magnetic%20bezel%20attachments%2C%20a%20flush%20mount%2C%20access%20to%20digital%20paintings%2C%20and%20a%20motion%20sensor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20like%20that%20Hisense%20offers%20a%20solid%20assortment%20of%20free%20paintings%20and%20photos%20without%20a%20membership.%20In%20fact%2C%20Hisense%20doesn't%20currently%20offer%20a%20premium%20subscription%20option.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20selection%20of%20photography%20and%20art%20prints%20isn't%20as%20wide%20as%20what%20you'd%20get%20with%20Samsung's%20paid%20Art%20Store%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20often%20trying%20to%20switch%20up%20the%20mood%20in%20your%20room%2C%20you%20won't%20have%20as%20many%20options.%20However%2C%20I%20never%20had%20that%20problem%20and%20found%20more%20than%20enough%20free%20choices%20that%20I%20liked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Hisense%20CanvasTV%20mounted%20on%20a%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f7515194a2d49b8aea8ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20CanvasTV's%20biggest%20downside%20is%20its%20lack%20of%20a%20connection%20box%2C%20which%20means%20wires%20to%20your%20connected%20devices%20will%20hang%20down%20from%20the%20display.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20complaint%20I%20have%20about%20the%20CanvasTV%20is%20that%20all%20of%20its%20connection%20ports%20are%20built%20into%20the%20back%20of%20the%20display%2C%20just%20like%20a%20traditional%20TV.%20This%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20Samsung's%20Frame%20models%2C%20which%20use%20a%20separate%20connection%20box.%20So%20if%20you%20have%20lots%20of%20media%20devices%20you%20want%20to%20hook%20up%2C%20you%20could%20be%20left%20with%20multiple%20cables%20hanging%20down%20your%20wall%2C%20which%20hurts%20the%20TV's%20ability%20to%20mimic%20a%20framed%20painting.%20Of%20course%2C%20you%20could%20hide%20cables%20with%20some%20sort%20of%20cover%20or%20by%20feeding%20them%20through%20your%20wall%20if%20you're%20able%20to%20do%20some%20drilling%2C%20but%20Samsung's%20solution%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20user-friendly%20and%20versatile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20plus%20side%2C%20I%20like%20that%20the%20TV%20comes%20with%20a%20magnetic%20bezel%20that%20looks%20like%20a%20wood%20frame.%20You'd%20have%20to%20pay%20extra%20for%20that%20when%20buying%20a%20Samsung%20model.%20However%2C%20alternate%20magnetic%20bezels%20are%20difficult%20to%20track%20down%20through%20Hisense%20or%20third-party%20retailers.%20The%20most%20common%20search%20results%20are%20for%20those%20from%20sellers%20on%20Etsy.%20In%20contrast%2C%20there%20are%20tons%20of%20styles%20available%20for%20Samsung%20Frame%20TVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20picture%20quality%2C%20there's%20not%20much%20separating%20the%20CanvasTV%20from%20the%20standard%20Frame.%20The%204K%20QLED%20display%20offers%20decent%20pop%20in%20both%20dark%20and%20light%20room%20conditions%20with%20similar%20brightness%20capabilities.%20Watching%20movies%20with%20the%20basic%20settings%20most%20people%20will%20use%2C%20I%20couldn't%20easily%20tell%20a%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20products%20when%20it%20came%20to%20black%20levels%20or%20color%20saturation.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20did%20find%20the%20CanvasTV's%20viewing%20angles%20to%20be%20more%20limited%2C%20especially%20when%20watching%20TV%20during%20the%20day%20in%20bright%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20with%20its%20drawbacks%2C%20Hisense's%20CanvasTV%20is%20the%20best%20Frame%20TV%20alternative%20for%20anyone%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20wants%20a%20more%20affordable%20art%20TV%20that%20mimics%20most%2C%20but%20not%20all%2C%20of%20the%20features%20you%20get%20on%20Samsung's%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224f377f8-5ba7-4c10-a525-be2bf14d750c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20on%20a%20budget%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20on%20a%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20its%20matte%20display%20and%20thin%20frame%2C%20the%20TCL%20NXTVISION%20is%20convincing%20enough%20as%20an%20art-style%20TV.%20It's%20missing%20some%20features%20found%20on%20the%20Samsung%20Frame%20and%20Hisense%20CanvasTV%2C%20but%20it%20earns%20some%20extra%20points%20in%20overall%20value.%20This%20model%20is%20often%20the%20most%20affordable%20art%20TV%20of%20the%20bunch%2C%20with%20frequent%20discounts%20bringing%20the%2065-inch%20model%20down%20to%20just%20under%20%24900.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NXTVISION%20TV%20comes%20with%20a%20light%20wood-style%20bezel%20that%20attaches%20easily%20with%20magnets.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20finding%20replacement%20colors%20or%20different%20options%20through%20online%20searches.%20This%20could%20change%2C%20but%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20Samsung%20has%20a%20clear%20advantage%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20bezel%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETCL%20offers%20100%2Bpieces%20of%20free%20art%20to%20display%20when%20the%20TV%20is%20off%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20screensaver-like%20choices%20with%20motion%20and%20the%20option%20to%20show%20details%20like%20the%20time.%20Though%20the%20selection%20is%20solid%2C%20it's%20smaller%20than%20those%20offered%20by%20Hisense's%20free%20gallery%20or%20Samsung's%20paid%20service.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20trouble%20finding%20art%20to%20use%2C%20but%20ask%20me%20again%20in%20a%20year%20or%20two%2C%20and%20the%20limited%20selection%20may%20be%20more%20of%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222308%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TCL%20NXTVISION%20TV%20on%20an%20eisel%20stand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5