s%20for%20her%20cats%20Salem%20and%20Luna.%20When%20Salem%20burrows%20inside%20and%20is%20jumped%20on%20by%20Luna%2C%20Lily%20can%20just%20reform%20the%20tunnel%20to%20reset%20the%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220797f3e2-7dfc-42e8-916a-c9e84fd6c7ea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20wand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20cat%20without%20toys%20isn't%20just%20bored%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20missing%20out%20on%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20being%20a%20cat.%20Without%20a%20way%20to%20act%20out%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ficatcare.org%2Farticles%2Funderstanding-the-hunting-behaviour-of-cats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20hunting%20sequence%3C%2Fa%3E%20(including%20stalking%2C%20capturing%2C%20and%20killing)%2C%20cats%20are%20deprived%20of%20behaviors%20as%20essential%20to%20them%20as%20daily%20movement%20is%20to%20us.%20Over%20time%2C%20that%20lack%20of%20stimulation%20can%20lead%20to%20stress%20and%20unwanted%20behaviors.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20conflicts%20that%20we%20see%20between%20cats%20or%20cats%20and%20people%20are%20stress-related%2C%26quot%3B%20Siracusa%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInteractive%20wand%20toys%20are%20an%20especially%20effective%20way%20to%20satisfy%20your%20cat's%20instincts%20and%20get%20them%20moving.%20Because%20you%20control%20the%20speed%20and%20direction%2C%20you%20can%20mimic%20the%20way%20prey%20would%20behave%2C%20like%20dancing%20away%20from%20your%20cat%20instead%20of%20moving%20toward%20them%2C%20Geller%20says.%20She%20recommends%20the%20Pet%20Fit%20For%20Life%20Wand%2C%20which%20has%20a%20plush%20foam%20handle%2C%20a%20metal%20wand%2C%20and%20an%20extra%20extension%20piece%20to%20make%20the%20wand%20even%20longer.%20That%20added%20reach%20keeps%20your%20hands%20safely%20out%20of%20the%20play%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cats%20playfully%20chase%20feather%20wand%20toys%20toys%20on%20hardwood%20and%20carpeted%20floors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f9dcdcfc04e97619b8898%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Fischer%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDifferent%20cats%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20the%20same%20cat%20on%20different%20days%20%E2%80%94%20will%20gravitate%20to%20different%20textures%20and%20movements%2C%20Siracusa%20says.%20In%20Geller's%20experience%20and%20for%20our%20tester's%20cats%2C%20the%20Pet%20Fit%20For%20Life%20feather%20attachment%20was%20the%20clear%20favorite%2C%20while%20my%20cats%20were%20just%20as%20excited%20about%20the%20worm.%20To%20cover%20all%20your%20bases%2C%20the%20Pet%20Fit%20For%20Life%20bundle%20comes%20with%20an%20easy-on%2Foff%20metal%20clasp%20and%20four%20interchangeable%20attachments%20%E2%80%94%20a%20worm%2C%20two%20feather%20attachments%2C%20and%20a%20mouse%20with%20feathers.%20Always%20put%20wand%20toys%20away%20between%20play%20sessions%20to%20prevent%20accidental%20tangles%20or%20chewing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d26a761-8906-4a8f-a249-c8ca957ddcc6%5C%22%3EBest%20mouse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMouse%20toys%20are%20a%20classic%20choice%20for%20cat%20parents%20because%20they%20look%20like%20a%20cat's%20most%20iconic%20prey.%20Our%20experts%20say%20that%20toys%20mimicking%20real%20prey%20in%20size%20and%20texture%20can%20spark%20your%20cat's%20hunting%20instincts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartz%20Cattraction%20with%20Silver%20Vine%20and%20Catnip%20Kitty%20Frenzy%20mice%20are%20the%20best%20mouse%20cat%20toys%20we%20tested%20because%20they're%20stuffed%20with%20catnip%20and%20silvervine%2C%20which%20trigger%20a%20burst%20of%20playful%20energy%20in%20many%20cats.%20After%20that%20initial%20excitement%20fades%2C%20cats%20often%20like%20to%20cuddle%20up%20with%20or%20even%20lick%20their%20%26quot%3Bprey%26quot%3B.%20These%20mice%20don't%20make%20a%20satisfying%20rattle%20when%20shaken%2C%20which%20would%20help%20to%20grab%20a%20cat's%20attention%20and%20spark%20their%20drive%20to%20chase.%20That%20said%2C%20no%20sound%20at%20all%20is%20often%20better%20than%20loud%20squeaks%2C%20especially%20for%20timid%20cats.%20%26quot%3BLoud%20electronic%20squeaks%20may%20frighten%20more%20than%20entice%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Aimee%20Warner%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20at%20Waggel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20plays%20with%20a%20small%20blue%20plush%20mouse%20toy%20on%20a%20carpeted%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e5229a17a8c5b4052e864%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConstructed%20from%20hollow%20plastic%20wrapped%20in%20soft%20fabric%2C%20they're%20sturdy%20yet%20lightweight%20enough%20for%20cats%20to%20carry%20or%20slide%20across%20floors.%20Rather%20than%20hard%20plastic%20eyes%20and%20nose%20that%20could%20come%20loose%20and%20be%20ingested%2C%20these%20mice%20feature%20soft%20felt%20pieces%20that%20are%20glued%20in%20place.%20I%20pulled%20firmly%20on%20the%20ears%2C%20tail%2C%20seams%2C%20and%20felt%20details%2C%20and%20everything%20stayed%20securely%20attached.%20%26quot%3BUsually%20cats%20try%20to%20grab%20the%20object%2C%20the%20prey%2C%20and%20run%20away%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Siracusa%20says.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20important%20that%20it%20is%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221781795-3652-46d3-9684-be04f72ff3ec%5C%22%3EBest%20automatic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20morning%2C%20my%20cat%20Atlas%20waits%20patiently%20for%20me%20to%20switch%20on%20her%20favorite%20toy%2C%20the%20Potaroma%203-in-1%20Hide-and-Seek%20Cat%20Toy.%20This%20has%20been%20part%20of%20her%20routine%20for%20over%20two%20years.%20We%20love%20it%20so%20much%20that%20I've%20gifted%20one%20to%20my%20brother-in-law's%20cats%20and%20recommended%20it%20to%20several%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20motorized%20butterfly%20that%20spins%20and%20flutters%20on%20top%20and%20a%20fluffy%20toy%20that%20circles%20unpredictably%20under%20a%20fabric%20cover.%20%26quot%3BMotorized%20'prey%20under%20fabric'%20mats%20invite%20low-impact%2C%20extended%20activity%20%E2%80%94%20perfect%20for%20calorie%20burn%20without%20joint%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20Warner%20says.%20The%20butterfly%20moves%20realistically%2C%20and%20the%20hidden%20toy%20pops%20out%20with%20an%20element%20of%20surprise.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20toy%20always%20moves%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20the%20cat%20will%20quickly%20realize%20it%20isn't%20real%20prey%20and%20lose%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.felidaebehavior.com%2Fabout-cat-behavior-consultant-heather-alvey%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeather%20Alvey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20certified%20cat%20behavior%20consultant%20and%20owner%20of%20Felidae%20Behavior%20Consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20plays%20with%20an%20interactive%20toy%20featuring%20a%20colorful%20butterfly%20and%20a%20spinning%20fabric%20skirt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e5259cfc04e97619b7321%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20automatic%20cat%20toys%20don't%20run%20endlessly%2C%20Siracusa%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20leave%20the%20game%20going%20and%20the%20cat%20can't%20grab%20anything%2C%20the%20cat%20will%20lose%20interest%20and%20might%20even%20become%20frustrated.%26quot%3B%20While%20cats%20can%20bite%20the%20butterfly%20and%20fluffy%20toy%2C%20the%20Potaroma%20also%20stops%20automatically%20after%20five%20minutes%20of%20inactivity.%20It%20stays%20in%20standby%20mode%20for%20two%20hours%2C%20so%20your%20cat%20can%20reactivate%20it%20with%20a%20touch.%20I%20typically%20charge%20it%20overnight%20abo