0part%20of%20the%20hunt.%20Geller%20recommends%20letting%20your%20cat%20successfully%20grab%20the%20toy%20in%20their%20mouth%20or%20paws%20before%20starting%20the%20game%20again.%20%26quot%3BReal%20prey%20might%20lose%20stamina%20during%20the%20hunt%20or%20play%20dead%20to%20trick%20the%20cat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20These%20little%20captures%20are%20what%20trigger%20feel-good%20chemicals.%20The%20soft%20cardboard%20also%20gives%20your%20cat%20something%20satisfying%20to%20bite%20or%20claw%2C%20fulfilling%20the%20%26quot%3Bkill%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20the%20hunt.%20Geller%20recommends%20letting%20your%20cat%20successfully%20grab%20the%20toy%20in%20their%20mouth%20or%20paws%20before%20starting%20the%20game%20again.%20%26quot%3BReal%20prey%20might%20lose%20stamina%20during%20the%20hunt%20or%20play%20dead%20to%20trick%20the%20cat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20These%20little%20captures%20are%20what%20trigger%20feel-good%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20gone%20through%20several%20Cat%20Dancers%20over%20the%20years%2C%20since%20determined%20cats%20can%20eventually%20rip%20the%20cardboard%20off.%20But%20for%20its%20low%20price%2C%20it's%20an%20easy%20toy%20to%20replace%20when%20the%20old%20one%20finally%20gives%20out.%20For%20a%20deeper%20dive%20into%20what%20makes%20it%20a%20fan%20fave%20for%20one%20editor's%20cat%2C%20check%20out%20our%20Cat%20Dancer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fcat-dancer-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c230e63b-69e7-413f-ac93-7d4bc90d5cce%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20ring%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20cats%20will%20turn%20just%20about%20anything%20into%20a%20toy%20%E2%80%94%20milk%20rings%2C%20bread%20ties%2C%20you%20name%20it.%20It's%20entertaining%20to%20see%20them%20get%20creative%2C%20and%20it%20might%20save%20you%20a%20few%20bucks%20on%20toys.%20But%20those%20household%20items%20aren't%20designed%20to%20hold%20up%20to%20rough%20play%20or%20a%20cat's%20teeth%20and%20claws.%20They%20can%20break%20into%20small%20pieces%20or%20cause%20an%20intestinal%20blockage.%20Fat%20Cat%20Cat%20Crazies%20are%20a%20safer%2C%20more%20durable%20alternative.%20These%20colorful%20rings%20skitter%20and%20slide%20across%20the%20floor%20like%20little%20bugs.%20I%20can%20twist%20and%20tug%20them%20without%20snapping%20them%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20years%20of%20tossing%20these%20rings%20across%20our%20house%2C%20I%20still%20haven't%20found%20a%20single%20broken%20one.%20My%20cat%20goes%20wild%20when%20they%20zip%20across%20the%20tile%20floor%2C%20sending%20her%20sliding%20after%20them%20on%20her%20furry%20paws.%20Sometimes%20I'll%20add%20the%20Ripple%20Rug%20to%20the%20mix%20so%20the%20ring%20skips%20over%20the%20carpet%20before%20gliding%20onto%20the%20hardwood.%20Your%20cat%20might%20even%20retrieve%20the%20ring%20and%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20you%2C%20ready%20for%20another%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20sits%20on%20a%20carpet%20with%20a%20yellow%20plastic%20Cat%20Crazies%20ring%20toy%20in%20front%20of%20its%20paws.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e5304cfc04e97619b732e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rings%20will%20definitely%20end%20up%20under%20your%20stove%20or%20couch%2C%20but%20at%20around%20%244%20for%20a%20pack%20of%20four%2C%20it's%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5436a4e-f0f0-4c73-8960-b334a15fc83a%5C%22%3EBest%20catnip%20kicker%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYeowww!%20is%20well-known%20for%20making%20cat%20kicker%20toys%20that%20many%20cats%20love.%20They%20use%20only%20catnip%20leaves%20and%20flower%20tops%20for%20maximum%20strength%20%E2%80%94%20a%20combination%20that%20revs%20many%20cats%20up.%20I%20especially%20like%20their%20rainbow%20and%20banana%20kickers%20because%20they%20have%20a%20slight%20curve.%20Warner%20says%20curved%20kickers%20hug%20the%20belly%2C%20making%20them%20easier%20for%20cats%20to%20grab%20and%20hold%20compared%20to%20straight%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20tester%20Chowder%20was%20particularly%20enthusiastic%20about%20her%20banana%20kicker.%20%26quot%3BShe%20likes%20to%20get%20super%20'high'%20on%20it%20and%20bounce%20around%20the%20house.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20she%20enjoys%20the%20catnip%20or%20the%20toy%20more%2C%20but%20she's%20having%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20her%20human%2C%20Lauren%20Savoie%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%20deputy%20executive%20editor.%20While%20my%20cats%20might%20not%20bounce%20around%20the%20room%20the%20house%20after%20playing%20with%20their%20rainbow%20kicker%2C%20they%20certainly%20enjoy%20intense%20bunny%20kicking%20sessions%2C%20often%20pausing%20to%20bite%20and%20lick%20the%20toy%20between%20kicks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20and%20white%20cat%20plays%20with%20a%20yellow%20banana-shaped%20catnip%20toy%20on%20a%20patterned%20rug.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e53b1cfc04e97619b733e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKicking%20with%20the%20back%20legs%20is%20a%20behavior%20cats%20will%20use%20with%20larger%20prey%2C%20like%20if%20they%20catch%20a%20rabbit%2C%26quot%3B%20Siracusa%20says.%20With%20all%20that%20kicking%20power%2C%20you%20need%20a%20kicker%20that's%20built%20to%20last.%20Yeowww!%20toys%20are%20made%20of%20sturdy%20twill%20with%20strong%20seams%2C%20and%20their%20catnip%20stays%20impressively%20potent.%20The%20best%20cat%20kicker%20toys%20are%20large%20enough%20for%20your%20cat%20to%20firmly%20grasp%20and%20kick%20with%20their%20back%20legs%2C%20about%208%20to%2010%20inches%2C%20Warner%20says.%20The%20Yeowww!%20rainbow%20and%20banana%20kickers%20measure%206%20and%207%20inches%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afdfb922-03f7-496c-8c52-50726ecf99c3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20crinkle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20crinkle%20balls%20have%20been%20a%20longtime%20favorite%20of%20our%20feline%20tester.%20They%20make%20a%20soft%20rustling%20sound%20and%20have%20an%20irresistible%20texture.%20%26quot%3BPapaya%20loves%20the%20noise%20these%20crinkle%20toys%20make!%20She%20especially%20enjoys%20when%20we%20squish%20them%20in%20our%20hands%20to%20create%20fun%20sounds%20before%20tossing%20them%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20batting%20and%20kicking%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20her%20human%2C%20Sally%20Kaplan%2C%20Insider%20Reviews%20executive%20editor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Siracusa%2C%20short%20bursts%20of%20play%20%E2%80%94%20about%20three%20to%20five%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20are%20ideal%20for%20cats.%20As%20soon%20as%20their%20interest%20starts%20to%20fade%2C%20it's%20the%20perfect%20moment%20to%20wrap%20up%20with%20a%20treat%20or%20a%20small%20meal%20for%20a%20satisfying%20%26quot%3Bgame%20over%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20hunting%20sequence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20gray%20and%20white%20cat%20plays%20with%20a%20crinkly%20toy%20on%20a%20patterned%20rug.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e5408cfc04e97619b7343%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20pack%20comes%20with%2012%20brightly%20colored%20crinkle%20balls.%20Papaya%20has%20been%20enjoying%20hers%20for%20years%20without%20any%20shredding%20or%20damage.%20Each%20ball%20measures%20about%201%201%2F2%20to%202%20inches%20in%20diameter%2C%20meeting%20Warner's%20safety%20guideline%20to%20avoid%20any%20toy%20smaller%20than%201%201%2F4%20inches%20across.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260950d7b-928b-417d-89ca-b1ab7f75fff5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20ball%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20your%20cat%20prefers%20a%20ball%20with%20a%20little%20more%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoomph%2C%20a%20ping%20pong%20ball%20might%20do%20the%20trick.%20I%20like%20to%20bounce%20them%20off%20the%20floor%20or%20send%20them%20rolling%20down%20the%20stairs.%20My%20cat%20Lyra%20will%20leap%20into%20the%20air%20trying%20to%20swat%20them%20down%2C%20and%20both%20cats%20love%20chasing%20them%20down%20the%20stairs%2C%20only%20for%20the%20balls%20to%20ricochet%20and%20bounce%20off%20in%20a%20new%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20is%20holding%20a%20ping%20pong%20ball%20in%20front%20of%20a%20white%20and%20gray%20cat%20that%20is%20standing%20on%20its%20hind%20legs%20to%20try%20to%20reach%20the%20ball.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f57f3194a2d49b8aea495%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPing%20pong%20balls%20aren't%20ideal%20if%20your%20cat%20wants%20to%20retrieve%20the%20toy%2C%20but%20they're%20a%20smart%20choice%20for%20cats%20who%20chew%20or%20try%20to%20ingest%20softer%20materials.%20Siracusa%20says%20if%20your%20cat%20happily%20bats%20and%20chases%20them%2C%20ping%20pong%20balls%20work%20well.%20You%20can%20also%20make%20an%20enrichment%20game%20for%20your%20cat%20by%20adding%20them%20to%20a%20cake%20pan%20filled%20with%20shallow%20water%2C%20creating%20an%20extra%20challenge%20when%20your%20cat%20tries%20to%20scoop%20them%20out%20from%20an%20unstable%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286832e52-408e-4581-95ea-a6755a22f48d%5C%22%3EBest%20food%20puzzle%20toy%20overall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDaily%20food%20enrichment%20is%20essential%20to%20the%20emotional%20well-being%20of%20cats%20and%20supports%20their%20natural%20behaviors%20of%20hunting%2C%20foraging%2C%20and%20eating%20multiple%20small%20meals.%20Food%20puzzle%20toys%20dispense%20food%20or%20treats%20when%20manipulated%20and%20allow%20cats%20to%20think%20through%20challenges%20in%20a%20physically%20active%20way%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smalldoorvet.com%2Fteam%2Fdr-jamie-richardson%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jamie%20Richardson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20head%20of%20veterinary%20medicine%20at%20Small%20Door%20Vet.%20Food%20puzzles%20range%20from%20beginner%20to%20expert%20levels%2C%20and%20Geller%20recommends%20the%20Nina%20Ottosson%20Rainy%20Day%20Puzzle%20and%20Play%20as%20an%20expert-level%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20but%20don't%20let%20that%20intimidate%20you%20or%20your%20cat.%20What%20I%20love%20about%20this%20puzzle%20is%20how%20adjustable%20it%20is%20to%20many%20skill%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20introduced%20this%20puzzle%20slowly%20to%20my%20less%20food-motivated%20cat%20Atlas%20to%20keep%20her%20engaged%20without%20frustrating%20her%2C%20which%20Siracusa%20says%20can%20look%20like%20giving%20up%20or%20walking%20away.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20placed%20kibble%20in%20the%20open%20wells%2C%20then%20started%20covering%20some%20with%20the%20swiveling%20raindrops.%20Once%20she%20got%20the%20hang%20of%20that%2C%20I%20added%20the%20spinning%20wheel.%20Now%20she's%20solving%20the%20scent%20peg%20challenge%2C%20which%20requires%20her%20to%20move%20the%20peg%20over%20the%20well%20to%20release%20the%20food%20within%2C%20then%20shift%20it%20again%20to%20reach%20the%20prize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20interacts%20with%20a%20treat%20puzzle%20board%20featuring%20sliding%20and%20rotating%20compartments.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e550ca17a8c5b4052e89b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20ways%20for%20your%20cat%20to%20use%20this%20puzzle%2C%20which%20is%20exactly%20what%20makes%20it%20such%20a%20worthwhile%20buy.%20Atlas%20has%20been%20working%20on%20it%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now%2C%20and%20it%20also%20works%20with%20wet%20food.%20On%20special%20occasions%2C%20we'll%20squeeze%20Churu%20treats%20into%20a%20few%20compartments.%20It%20has%20no%20removable%20parts%2C%20which%20can%20easily%20become%20lost.%20The%20shallow%20wells%20and%20raindrop%20shapes%20take%20a%20little%20extra%20effort%20to%20scrub%20with%20a%20sponge%2C%20but%20I%20find%20it%20easier%20to%20clean%20than%20other%20puzzles%20we've%20tried%20with%20narrow%20tubes%20or%20deep%20ridges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bae0cce-752a-47d3-bba6-71efd94251c1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20easy%20food%20puzzle%20toy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20this%20puzzle%20is%20ideal%20for%20beginners%20or%20cats%20who%20get%20frustrated%20by%20moving%20parts%2C%20your%20cat%20will%20still%20have%20to%20work%20for%20their%20reward.%20The%20three-tiered%20Catit%20Senses%20Food%20Tree%20encourages%20them%20to%20sit%20up%2C%20paw%2C%20and%20bat%20for%20their%20food.%20They%20may%20even%20need%20to%20circle%20around%20it%20to%20find%20the%20best%20angle%20to%20reach%20their%20treats.%20Siracusa%20says%20some%20of%20the%20best%20food%20puzzles%20for%20cats%20are%20the%20ones%20that%20get%20them%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20use%20this%20puzzle%2C%20pour%20kibble%20or%20crunchy%20treats%20into%20the%20top.%20As%20the%20pieces%20fall%20through%2C%20they%20land%20within%20the%20staggered%20levels%2C%20which%20feature%20slots.%20It's%20up%20to%20your%20cat%20to%20reach%20in%20through%20small%20holes%20to%20pull%20the%20food%20out%20or%20push%20it%20downward%2C%20level%20by%20level%2C%20until%20it%20finally%20drops%20into%20the%20dish%20at%20the%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20uses%20its%20paw%20to%20retrieve%20kibble%20from%20a%20green%20Catit%20food%20puzzle%20feeder.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e54b0194a2d49b8ae9a42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20Tree%20doesn't%20work%20with%20wet%20food%2C%20but%20the%20openings%20are%20large%20enough%20to%20fit%20many%20kinds%20and%20sizes%20of%20treats%20and%20kibbles.%20It's%20easy%20to%20take%20apart%20and%20wash%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f17a86d-230c-40dd-a3d1-c8db842dbff0%5C%22%3EBest%20ball%20on%20track%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECats%20often%20lose%20interest%20in%20toys%20when%20they%20move%20too%20repetitively%20or%20predictably.%20%26quot%3BUnpredictable%20movement%20is%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.underdogcommunityproject.org%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Sarah%20Cortright%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20chief%20medical%20director%20of%20the%20Under%20Dog%20Community%20Project.%20Still%2C%20lower-energy%20adults%2C%20cats%20with%20mobility%20challenges%2C%20and%20kittens%20may%20enjoy%20the%20low%20impact%20of%20ball%20track%20toys%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20saw%20firsthand%20while%20fostering%20a%20semi-socialized%20cat%20who'd%20just%20given%20birth%20to%20five%20kittens.%20She%20was%20exhausted%20and%20wary%20of%20people%2C%20and%20no%20toy%20seemed%20to%20catch%20her%20eye.%20That%20is%2C%20until%20one%20day%2C%20I%20heard%20the%20rhythmic%20clack%20of%20the%20roller%20ball%20track%20toy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Catstages%20Chase%20Meowtain%20features%20four%20circular%20tiers%2C%20each%20with%20a%20lightweight%20plastic%20ball%20that%20circles%20its%20track.%20Some%20cats%20like%20to%20lie%20on%20their%20sides%20and%20lazily%20bat%20the%20balls%2C%20like%20my%20foster%20kitty.%20Others%20sit%20and%20paw%20at%20them%2C%20watching%20and%20waiting%20for%20the%20ball%20to%20circle%20the%20track%20for%20the%20next%20swat.%20More%20engaged%20cats%20might%20walk%20or%20sprint%20around%20the%20pyramid%20for%20a%20more%20active%20play%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20sits%20beside%20a%20tiered%20ball%20track%20toy%20with%20colorful%20rolling%20balls.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e5543194a2d49b8ae9a4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20balls%20aren't%20removable%20from%20the%20track%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20risk%20of%20losing%20them%20under%20the%20couch.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20are%20no%20small%20or%20removable%20parts%2C%20wires%2C%20or%20strings%2C%20which%20makes%20this%20one%20of%20the%20best%20cat%20toys%20to%20leave%20out%20for%20solo%20play.%20It%20has%20non-slip%20feet%2C%20though%20it%20still%20slides%20around%20a%20bit%20on%20hard%20surfaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221dd2210b-9a69-4bfc-beef-528224059a1e%5C%22%3EBest%20tunnel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wild%2C%20cats%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20stalking%20their%20prey%20and%20pouncing%20at%20them%20from%20under%20cover.%20A%20cat%20tunnel%20can%20create%20that%20feeling%20for%20your%20cat%2C%20down%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20tall%20grass%20subtly%20rustling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20cats%20race%20through%20the%20Kitty%20City%20Cat%20Tunnel%20Bed%2C%20it%20rustles%20just%20enough%20to%20mimic%20the%20thrill%20of%20sneaking%20through%20vegetation.%20It%20has%20two%20entrances%2C%20each%20with%20a%20dangling%20toy%2C%20though%20my%20cats%20are%20usually%20too%20busy%20stalking%20and%20pouncing%20on%20passing%20wands%20and%20teasers%20to%20pay%20them%20much%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20underestimate%20the%20importance%20of%20interactive%20play%20alongside%20the%20tunnel.%20You%20don't%20want%20your%20movement%20to%20be%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20looks%20like%20live%20prey%2C%20Siracusa%20says.%20A%20tunnel%20offers%20cats%20a%20place%20to%20hide%20and%20plan%20ambushes%2C%20but%20it's%20up%20to%20you%20to%20direct%20that%20hunting%20instinct%20toward%20toys%20%E2%80%94%20not%20your%20feet%20or%20ankles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20plays%20inside%20a%20red%20and%20blue%20plaid%20tunnel%2C%20reaching%20a%20paw%20out%20through%20the%20opening.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e5b7fa17a8c5b4052e8e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20%26quot%3Bhunt%26quot%3B%20is%20over%2C%20reward%20your%20cat%20with%20a%20treat%20before%20allowing%20them%20to%20curl%20up%20in%20the%20cozy%20bed%20at%20the%20tunnel's%20center%20before%20the%20next%20hunt.%20The%20Kitty%20City%20Cat%20Tunnel%20Bed%20also%20took%20top%20honors%20in%20the%20tunnel%20category%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-bed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguide%20to%20the%20best%20cat%20beds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20it%20won%20praise%20for%20its%20versatility%20and%20dual%20uses%20for%20lounging%20and%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298823420-2e80-44b6-b869-b74fb67cbe40%5C%22%3EBest%20subscription%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20made%20it%20to%20the%20end%20of%20this%20best%20cat%20toys%20roundup%20and%20still%20feel%20unsure%20where%20to%20start%20%E2%80%94%20or%20if%20it%20seems%20like%20your%20cat%20doesn't%20like%20anything%20you've%20tried%20%E2%80%94%20a%20subscription%20box%20can%20be%20a%20smart%20way%20to%20discover%20what%20excites%20them.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20give%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Siracusa.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20just%20try%20one%20or%20two%20toys%20because%20they're%20popular.%20If%20your%20cat%20doesn't%20like%20them%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20We're%20all%20different%2C%20and%20cats%20are%20too.%26quot%3B%20Even%20if%20you%20don't%20stick%20with%20it%20long-term%2C%20a%20few%20deliveries%20can%20help%20pinpoint%20your%20cat's%20play%20style.%20If%20you%20do%20find%20toys%20that%20are%20a%20hit%20with%20your%20cat%2C%20rotating%20toys%20every%20few%20days%20can%20help%20maintain%20novelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20KitNipBox%2C%20five%20new%20cat%20items%20arrive%20monthly%2C%20with%205%25%20of%20the%20proceeds%20supporting%20animal%20welfare.%20You%20can%20pick%20larger%20boxes%20if%20you'd%20like%20more%20toys%2C%20and%20cancel%20anytime%20before%20the%20next%20charge.%20The%20variety%20and%20quality%20of%20toys%20in%20my%20first%20box%20really%20impressed%20me%2C%20and%20my%20cats%20were%20instantly%20drawn%20to%20all%20of%20them.%20The%20second%20box%2C%20however%2C%20was%20less%20exciting%2C%20with%20fewer%20unique%20toys%2C%20though%20Atlas%20still%20happily%20purred%20as%20I%20unpacked%20it.%20While%20this%20suggests%20the%20boxes%20may%20lack%20variety%20some%20months%2C%20all%20the%20toys%20are%20designed%20in-house%2C%20which%20makes%20each%20box%20feel%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cat%20explores%20a%20KitNipBox%20filled%20with%20colorful%20toys%20and%20treats.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e55ef194a2d49b8ae9a53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20Happy%20Cat%20Box%2C%20intended%20for%20one%20cat%2C%20included%20a%20two-pack%20of%20'90s-inspired%20catnip-filled%20hair%20scrunchies%2C%20a%20sisal%20and%20raffia%20chew%20toy%20(Lyra%20went%20straight%20for%20this)%2C%20two%20strong%20catnip%20kickers%2C%20and%20a%20wand%20with%20a%20long%20ribbon%2C%20bell%2C%20and%20sturdy%20wooden%20handle%20(my%20cats'%20favorite).%20The%20featured%20treats%20were%20Vitakraft%20lick%20treats%20made%20with%20salmon%20broth%2C%20salmon%2C%20and%20other%20meats%2C%20and%20just%208%20calories%20each.%20A%20lick%20mat%20was%20included%20for%20serving%2C%20but%20you%20can%20swap%20the%20treats%20for%20an%20extra%20toy%20instead.%20The%20second%20box%20was%20packed%20mostly%20with%20plush%20kicker%20toys%2C%20one%20of%20them%20filled%20with%20catnip%2C%20plus%20crunchy%20Emerald%20Pet%20Feline%20Dental%20Treats.%20Despite%20the%20lack%20of%20variety%20in%20my%20second%20box%2C%20it's%20worth%20giving%20KitNip%20a%20chance%20if%20you're%20striking%20out%20elsewhere%2C%20don't%20know%20where%20to%20start%2C%20or%20just%20want%20to%20mix%20things%20up%20for%20your%20cat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adf1f85b-278a-4367-b7b3-468051ec0b28%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20cat%20toys%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%26quot%3Btoys%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20fully%20capture%20how%20important%20playthings%20are%20for%20cats.%20%26quot%3BPlayful%20behavior%20is%20something%20that%20is%20part%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20cats%20themselves%2C%20because%20it%20allows%20them%20to%20kill%20animals%20multiple%20times%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Siracusa%20says.%20My%20experts%20recommend%20choosing%20toys%20that%20spark%20your%20cat's%20hunting%20instincts.%20This%20way%2C%20they%20can%20complete%20their%20%26quot%3Bhunt%26quot%3B%20and%20won't%20seek%20out%20other%2C%20less%20desirable%20activities%20or%20outlets.%20Here%20are%20the%20key%20qualities%20of%20the%20best%20cat%20toys%20to%20help%20channel%20your%20cat's%20instincts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiologically%20appropriate%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Experts%20agree%20that%20the%20best%20cat%20toys%20tap%20into%20a%20cat's%20instinct%20to%20hunt.%20When%20evaluating%20a%20toy%2C%20consider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMovement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Does%20it%20move%20sporadically%20and%20realistically%2C%20or%20can%20you%20manipulate%20the%20toy%20to%20mimic%20the%20motion%20of%20prey%3F%20%26quot%3BThe%20best%20automated%20toys%20move%20erratically%2C%20stop%20and%20start%2C%20or%20hide%20under%20fabric%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20mouse%20scurrying%20under%20a%20blanket%2C%26quot%3B%20Cortright%20says.%20Automatic%20toys%20should%20also%20be%20designed%20to%20be%20caught%20by%20the%20cat%20to%20prevent%20frustration.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20best%20teasers%20and%20wands%2C%20look%20for%20wires%20that%20bounce%20or%20feathers%20that%20flutter.%20%26quot%3BPrey%20doesn't%20dangle%20in%20a%20cat's%20face%20or%20bop%20them%20on%20the%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Alvey%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFunctionality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Does%20the%20toy%20inspire%20stalking%2C%20chasing%2C%20pouncing%2C%20biting%2C%20foraging%2C%20or%20hiding%3F%20These%20are%20all%20important%20activities%20that%20allow%20your%20cat%20to%20be%20a%20cat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Does%20it%20resemble%20real%20prey%20in%20size%2C%20shape%2C%20or%20texture%3F%20Look%20for%20fur-like%20fabric%2C%20feathers%2C%20or%20crinkly%20materials.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurprise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Are%20there%20moving%20or%20disappearing%20elements%2C%20like%20toys%20that%20pop%20out%20from%20fabric%20or%20tunnels%3F%20%26quot%3BPredictability%20is%20a%20fast%20death%20for%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20Warner%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20and%20durability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECat%20toys%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20hunted%20and%20%26quot%3Bkilled%26quot%3B%20through%20chasing%2C%20pouncing%2C%20biting%2C%20and%20kicking%2C%20so%20they%20need%20to%20hold%20up%20to%20rough%20play.%20According%20to%20my%20experts%2C%20these%20safety%20guidelines%20will%20help%20keep%20your%20cat%20safer%20while%20playing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChoose%20toys%20without%20small%20parts%20like%20beaded%20eyes%2C%20noses%2C%20or%20foam%20pieces.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheck%20seams%20and%20parts%20regularly%20by%20gently%20pulling%20on%20them.%20Toss%20any%20toy%20with%20loose%20pieces%20or%20exposed%20stuffing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAvoid%20toys%20smaller%20than%201%20%C2%BC%20inches%20in%20diameter%2C%20Warner%20says.%20Anything%20smaller%20can%20be%20swallowed%20and%20cause%20choking%20or%20a%20blockage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStore%20anything%20with%20long%20strings%20out%20of%20reach%20(like%20wands)%20until%20supervised%20playtime.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESafer%20options%20for%20solo%20play%20include%20catnip%20kickers%2C%20soft%20mice%2C%20and%20rubber%20balls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuitability%20for%20your%20cat's%20age%20and%20physical%20abilities%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESiracusa%20says%20kittens%20prefer%20social%20play%20%E2%80%94%20like%20chasing%2C%20wrestling%2C%20and%20mock%20fighting%20%E2%80%94%20but%20few%20toys%20truly%20replicate%20that.%20A%20simple%20mouse%20toy%20can%20come%20close%20for%20kittens%20who%20like%20to%20retrieve.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20adult%20cats%20develop%20their%20own%20hunting%20styles%20and%20usually%20prefer%20object%20play%2C%20using%20toy%20objects%20to%20practice%20their%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20an%20aging%20cat%20or%20a%20cat%20with%20mobility%20issues%2C%20you'll%20likely%20need%20to%20adjust%20both%20the%20toys%20you%20choose%20and%20how%20you%20play.%20A%20senior%20cat%20with%20arthritis%20in%20their%20back%20legs%2C%20for%20example%2C%20may%20not%20want%20to%20bunny%20kick%20a%20catnip%20toy%20or%20jump%20after%20a%20wand.%20Warner%20says%20in%20these%20cases%2C%20try%20low-impact%20toys%20like%20treat%20balls%2C%20slow-feed%20puzzles%2C%20and%20motorized%20%26quot%3Bprey%20under%20fabric%26quot%3B%20mats.%20You%20can%20also%20adapt%20your%20wand%20play%20by%20scooting%20the%20toy%20under%20a%20blanket%20or%20engaging%20your%20cat%20with%20slow%2C%20low%20movements%20of%20the%20toy%20so%20your%20senior%20isn't%20forced%20to%20overextend%20their%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiracusa%20says%20a%20change%20in%20how%20often%20or%20how%20engaged%20a%20cat%20is%20in%20play%20can%20be%20a%20normal%20part%20of%20aging.%20However%2C%20any%20sudden%20changes%20in%20play%20or%20activity%20level%20should%20be%20discussed%20with%20your%20veterinarian.%20He%20says%20diseases%20as%20common%20as%20dental%20disease%20can%20make%20play%20painful%20for%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnticing%20extras%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20plants%2C%20including%20catnip%2C%20silvervine%2C%20and%20valerian%2C%20release%20chemicals%20meant%20to%20keep%20plant-eating%20insects%20away.%20But%20for%20cats%2C%20the%20effect%20is%20anything%20but%20threatening.%20Sniffing%20it%20sends%20many%20cats%20into%20a%20state%20of%20joy%3A%20rubbing%20their%20heads%20on%20objects%2C%20rolling%20around%2C%20and%20purring%20in%20what%20scientists%20dub%20the%20%26quot%3Bcatnip%20response.%26quot%3B%20Not%20every%20cat%20feels%20the%20same%20euphoria%20from%20catnip.%20However%2C%20our%20experts%20say%20fresh%20dried%20buds%20and%20cut%20leaves%20are%20often%20more%20exciting%20than%20powdered%20catnip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESound%20and%20texture%20matter%2C%20too.%20Crinkle%20materials%20can%20mimic%20the%20rustling%20of%20prey%20through%20grass%2C%20triggering%20a%20cat's%20hunting%20instincts.%20The%20texture%20adds%20tactile%20interest.%20However%2C%20loud%20squeakers%20or%20motors%20could%20be%20scary%20rather%20than%20fun%20to%20some%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b39fd29-4d8c-48ed-abc6-b836c9833dcb%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20cat%20toys%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20assortment%20of%20cat%20toys%20and%20activity%20puzzles%20is%20spread%20out%20around%20a%20labeled%20toy%20basket.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e5631cfc04e97619b7369%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20lifelong%20cat%20parent%2C%20including%20one%20cat%20with%20orthopedic%20issues%2C%20and%20I've%20fostered%20nearly%2050%20cats%20and%20kittens.%20I%20know%20firsthand%20how%20selective%20cats%20can%20be%2C%20and%20how%20rough%20they%20can%20be%20on%20their%20toys.%20To%20get%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20opinions%2C%20I%20recruited%20six%20Insider%20Reviews%20editors%20and%20reporters%20and%20their%20cats%20to%20help%20test%20the%20best%20cat%20toys.%20We%20tested%20over%2030%20cat%20toys%2C%20taking%20note%20of%20their%20features%2C%20our%20cats'%20level%20of%20enthusiasm%2C%20and%20how%20they%20held%20up%20to%20play.%20Some%20toys%20were%20tested%20in%20multiple%20households.%20Here's%20the%20approach%20we%20took%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20and%20Durability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20inspected%20every%20toy%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20checking%20for%20small%20parts%2C%20glued-on%20pieces%2C%20or%20fabric%20trim%20that%20could%20come%20loose.%20We%20gently%20tugged%20on%20any%20attachments%20to%20see%20if%20they%20detached%20easily.%20For%20soft%20or%20fabric%20toys%2C%20we%20pulled%20and%20twisted%20them%20to%20test%20the%20seams%20and%20stitching.%20We%20also%20bent%20or%20lightly%20compressed%20plastic%20components%20to%20see%20if%20they%20cracked%2C%20warped%2C%20or%20popped%20apart.%20For%20electronic%20toys%2C%20we%20let%20the%20battery%20run%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20measure%20battery%20life%2C%20then%20noted%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20recharge.%20During%20play%2C%20we%20watched%20closely%20for%20wear%20and%20tear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiologically%20appropriate%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBased%20on%20expert%20advice%2C%20we%20awarded%20points%20to%20toys%20that%20triggered%20a%20cat's%20hunting%20instincts%2C%20such%20as%20ones%20that%20wiggled%2C%20fluttered%2C%20or%20moved%20erratically.%20We%20checked%20each%20design%20to%20see%20if%20it%20looked%20like%20real%20prey%20in%20size%2C%20shape%2C%20or%20texture.%20We%20preferred%20toys%20with%20details%20like%20feathers%2C%20fur-like%20fabric%2C%20or%20a%20crinkly%20feel.%20Finally%2C%20we%20also%20gave%20high%20marks%20to%20toys%20that%20offered%20an%20element%20of%20surprise%2C%20like%20components%20that%20popped%20out%20from%20tunnels%20or%20disappeared%20under%20fabric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESubscription%20boxes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20addition%20to%20evaluating%20the%20toys%20themselves%2C%20I%20evaluated%20each%20cat%20toy%20subscription%20based%20on%20ease%20of%20sign-up%2C%20customization%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20swap%20toys%20for%20other%20toys%20or%20treats.%20I%20also%20checked%20whether%20the%20service%20provided%20clear%20shipping%20and%20delivery%20notifications%20and%20whether%20you%20could%20easily%20pause%20deliveries%20or%20cancel%20the%20subscription.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfe0c887-c45a-4673-b945-8a03d305822a%5C%22%3ECat%20toys%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tabby%20cat%20lies%20on%20the%20floor%20playing%20with%20a%20small%20blue%20toy%20with%20string%20attached.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e566d194a2d49b8ae9a66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Chase%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20toys%20do%20cats%20like%20the%20most%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPlay%20is%20all%20about%20hunting%2C%20so%20the%20best%20cat%20toys%20are%20ones%20that%20look%2C%20move%2C%20smell%2C%20and%2For%20sound%20like%20real%20prey.%20%26quot%3BWand%20toys%2C%20crinkle%20balls%2C%20and%20kicker%20toys%20are%20among%20the%20most%20popular%20cat%20toys%2C%26quot%3B%20Cortright%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20toys%20are%20best%20for%20indoor%20cats%3F%3C%2Fst