ound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292ad592c-afbb-4068-b957-93b96410dfac%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20it%20works%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecipes%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEach%20of%20Ollie's%20five%20Fresh%20recipes%20is%20made%20with%20100%25%20whole%20food%20and%20for%20all%20life%20stages%2C%20from%20puppies%20to%20older%20dogs.%20Each%20formula%20is%20made%20with%20a%20whole%20meat%20protein%20base%20%E2%80%94%20beef%2C%20chicken%2C%20turkey%2C%20lamb%2C%20or%20pork%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20a%20combination%20of%20fruit%2C%20veggies%2C%20and%20grains.%20There's%20no%20salmon%20option%2C%20but%20Ollie%20adds%20salmon%20oil%20to%20all%20of%20their%20recipes.%20Research%20shows%20that%20fish%20oil%20offers%20many%20health-boosting%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Ollie's%20recipes%20meet%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aafco.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Association%20of%20Feed%20Control%20Officials%3C%2Fa%3E%20(AAFCO)%20nutritional%20standards%20for%20puppies%20and%20adult%20dogs.%20That%20said%2C%20without%20a%20full-time%20veterinary%20nutritionist%20(the%20brand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.myollie.com%2Fhow-ollies-fresh-food-meets-and-exceeds-wsava-guidelines-on-selecting-pet-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsults%20with%20two%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionists%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20they%20don't%20fulfill%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwsava.org%2Fglobal-guidelines%2Fglobal-nutrition-guidelines%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Nutrition%20Guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwsava.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Small%20Animal%20Veterinary%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20(WSAVA).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ERecipe%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EIngredient%20highlights%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EGuaranteed%20a