%20either%20full%20fresh%2C%20half%20fresh%20(which%20you'd%20mix%20with%20their%20current%20food)%2C%20or%20a%20mixed%20plan%20of%20Ollie's%20fresh%20recipes%20and%20its%20baked%20kibble.%20For%20all%20options%2C%20you%20can%20also%20select%20up%20to%20four%20out%20of%20the%20five%20fresh%20food%20recipe%20options%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20add-ons%2C%20such%20as%20Ollie-branded%20treats%20and%20supplement%20chews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustomization%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBased%20on%20the%20initial%20screening%2C%20you're%20able%20to%20select%20one%20of%20three%20potential%20meal%20plans%3A%20full%20fresh%2C%20half%20fresh%2C%20or%20a%20mixed%20plan.%20Within%20each%20of%20these%2C%20you%20can%20customize%20which%20fresh%20recipes%20you%20want%20(up%20to%20four)%20and%20which%20baked%20recipes%2C%20if%20applicable.%20There%20are%20five%20fresh%20recipes%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20each%20with%20a%20different%20protein%20base%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20customize%20ingredients%20in%20the%20recipes%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20note%20if%20your%20dog%20has%20a%20sensitivity%20or%20allergy%2C%20such%20as%20to%20grains%2C%20the%20ordering%20process%20doesn't%20explicitly%20tell%20you%20which%20formulas%20have%20potential%20triggers.%20Instead%2C%20you%20have%20to%20click%20%26quot%3Bview%20ingredients%26quot%3B%20to%20see%2C%20though%20they%20do%20make%20this%20easy%20to%20spot%20and%20access%20in%20the%20customization%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelivery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYour%20first%20Ollie%20order%20takes%20around%20six%20days%20to%20ship%2C%20and%20then%20another%20one%20to%20two%20days%20to%20be%20delivered%2C%20so%20seven%20to%20eight%20days%20total.%20After%20your%20initial%20order%2C%20Ollie%20runs%20on%20a%20recurring%20subscription%20at%20the%20default%20of%20every%20two%20weeks.%20If%20you%20need%20your%20pup's%20food%20delivered%20sooner%20than%20planned%2C%20you%20can%20go%20into%20your%20account%20and%20click%20%26quot%3Bship%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20delivered%20within%20two%20to%20five%20days.%20While%20two%20weeks'%20worth%20of%20delivery%20is%20the%20default%2C%20you%20can%20also%20opt%20to%20have%20a%20larger%20supply%20delivered%20every%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPackaging%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOllie's%20fresh%20food%20is%20packaged%20as%20a%20plastic-wrapped%20food%20brick%2C%20which%20is%20frozen%20and%20shipped%20inside%20a%20medium-sized%20cardboard%20box%20with%20a%20Climacell%20cooler%20inside%2C%20covered%20with%20dry%20ice%20bags.%20The%20frozen%20food%20bricks%20are%20stacked%20inside%20the%20cooler%2C%20and%20this%20overall%20setup%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20keeping%20the%20food%20frozen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20your%20first%20shipment%2C%20you'll%20also%20get%20a%20welcome%20kit%20which%20includes%20a%20silicone%20food%20storage%20container%20that%20perfectly%20fits%20two%20food%20bricks%2C%20a%20plastic%20food%20scoop%2C%20and%20a%20pamphlet%20outlining%20how%20to%20best%20switch%20your%20dog%20to%20their%20new%20food%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20first%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217259efa-10be-4e84-8350-0550b68896de%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20Ollie%20dog%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20placing%20my%20Ollie%20order%2C%20I%20received%20emails%20with%20tracking%20info%20and%20an%20estimated%20shipping%20and%20delivery%20timeline.%20My%20box%20arrived%20a%20day%20earlier%20than%20expected%2C%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20and%20sat%20on%20my%20porch%20overnight%20in%20June%2C%20so%20I%20felt%20mildly%20stressed.%20But%20I%20opened%20the%20box%20the%20next%20morning%20to%20find%20all%2028%20of%20my%20fresh%20food%20bricks%20still%20fully%20frozen%20%E2%80%94%20a%20true%20testament%20to%20Ollie's%20packing%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20dry%20ice%20on%20top%20of%20the%20cooler%20was%20packed%20in%20disposable%20plastic%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20find%20the%20Climacell%20cooler%20was%20recyclable%2C%20and%20the%20cardboard%20box%2C%20too%2C%20of%20course.%20The%2028%20frozen%20bricks%20stacked%20nicely%20in%20my%20freezer%2C%20taking%20up%20about%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20space%20in%20my%20standard%20top-door%20freezer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20a%20frozen%20package%20of%20Ollie%20%26quot%3BPork%20Dish%20with%20Apples%26quot%3B%20dog%20food%20in%20front%20of%20a%20neatly%20stacked%20supply%20of%20similar%20packages%20inside%20a%20freezer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f4d70194a2d49b8aea33c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bricks%20of%20frozen%20food%20fit%20neatly%20in%20my%20freezer%20where%20I%20stacked%20them.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20Ollie%20order%20came%20with%20a%20silicone%20container%20to%20hold%20two%20food%20bricks%20side%20by%20side%20while%20they%20defrost%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20paddle%20to%20chop%20the%20food%20up.%20At%20first%2C%20the%20container%20seemed%20like%20a%20nice%20but%20unnecessary%20touch.%20Two%20days%20in%2C%20I%20realized%20its%20real%20value%3A%20Sure%2C%20it%20caught%20any%20melting%20ice%20before%20it%20could%20puddle%20on%20my%20fridge%20shelf%20and%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20stack%20other%20containers%20around%20Croc's%20defrosting%20meals.%20But%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20served%20as%20a%20visual%20reminder%20to%20keep%20the%20food%20rotation%20on%20track.%20Croc%20eats%20one%20brick%20per%20meal%2C%20so%20I%20always%20needed%20one%20defrosting%20for%20serving%20in%2024%20hours%20and%20another%20partially%20defrosted%20and%20ready%20in%2012.%20The%20new%20house%20rule%20became%20two%20bricks%20in%20the%20container%20at%20all%20times.%20If%20you%20take%20one%20out%2C%20replace%20it.%20Ollie%20recommends%20a%2024-hour%20defrost%2C%20which%20I%20found%20spot-on%2C%20and%20many%20were%20even%20ready%20in%2020.%20The%20food%20is%20good%20for%20up%20to%20four%20days%20once%20thawed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20looked%20a%20lot%20like%20ground-up%20human%20food%20with%20small%20chunks%20of%20recognizable%20ingredients%20like%20sweet%20potatoes%20and%20spinach%20%E2%80%94%20reassuring%20proof%20of%20the%20100%25%20fresh%20promise.%20I%20was%20especially%20pleased%20to%20find%20the%20food%20didn't%20smell%2C%20unlike%20Croc's%20regular%20dehydrated%20food.%20Its%20texture%20was%20also%20perfect.%20It%20crumbled%20easily%20with%20the%20included%20paddle%20or%20a%20fork%2C%20but%20was%20just%20sticky%20enough%20that%20I%20didn't%20lose%20pieces%20when%20transferring%20it%20from%20the%20package%20to%20the%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Ollie%20package%20of%20fresh%20dog%20food%20and%20a%20sealed%20Ollie%20package%20in%20a%20pink%20container%20sit%20on%20a%20dark%20countertop%20beside%20a%20stainless%20steel%20bowl%20filled%20with%20crumbled%20dog%20food%20and%20a%20pink%20scoop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f4e14cfc04e97619b7c70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20convenient%20to%20serve%20Ollie's%20fresh%20recipes%2C%20although%20I%20found%20it%20easier%20to%20use%20a%20kitchen%20utensil%20rather%20than%20the%20included%20paddle.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETransitioning%20Croc%20over%20to%20Ollie's%20food%20was%20relatively%20easy%20using%20the%20included%20pamphlet.%20It%20says%20you%20should%20slowly%20integrate%20the%20new%20food%20into%20the%20old%20in%20quarter%20increments%20over%20seven%20days.%20At%20that%20pace%2C%20Croc%20didn't%20have%20any%20digestive%20unease%20or%20discomfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20she%20was%20overjoyed%20at%20the%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECroc%20has%20always%20been%20food-motivated%20and%20is%20generally%20a%20fan%20of%20her%20usual%20The%20Honest%20Kitchen%20Dehydrated%20meals%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20over%20kibble%20%E2%80%94%20but%20her%20reaction%20to%20Ollie's%20fresh%20food%20was%20next%20level.%20After%20just%20two%20transition%20meals%20with%20one-quarter%20Ollie%20Fresh%2C%20she%20was%20already%20more%20alert%20during%20food%20prep.%20Once%20she%20was%20fully%20switched%20over%2C%20she'd%20sit%20beside%20me%20as%20I%20opened%20the%20package%20(I%20let%20her%20lick%20the%20empty%20container%20one%20time%20and%20created%20a%20monster).%20Then%20she'd%20literally%20sprint%20to%20her%20feeding%20area%20as%20I%20carried%20the%20bowl.%20We're%20typically%20strict%20with%20her%20mealtime%20manners%2C%20and%20she%20waits%20on%20her%20bed%20until%20released%2C%20but%20Ollie%20had%20her%20sneaking%20back%20underfoot%20in%20case%20of%20dropped%20crumbs%2C%20then%20racing%20to%20wait%20obediently%20for%20her%20Ollie%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20brown%20and%20white%20dog%20eats%20from%20a%20pink-rimmed%20stainless%20steel%20bowl%20filled%20with%20Ollie%20fresh%20dog%20food%20on%20a%20wooden%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f4e89cfc04e97619b7c87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECroc%20approved%20of%20all%20four%20of%20the%20Ollie%20fresh%20recipes%20she%20tried.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20seemed%20to%20enjoy%20all%20the%20recipes%20equally%3A%20beef%20with%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20lamb%20with%20cranberries%2C%20pork%20with%20apples%2C%20and%20turkey%20with%20blueberries.%20I%20liked%20that%20I%20could%20select%20specific%20proteins%20since%20she's%20intolerant%20to%20chicken%20(the%20fifth%20recipe%20option)%2C%20and%20I%20especially%20appreciated%20having%20four%20distinct%20formulas%20to%20rotate%20through.%20With%20her%20usual%20dehydrated%20food%2C%20even%20though%20it%20has%20varied%20ingredients%2C%20I've%20always%20felt%20her%20gut%20would%20benefit%20from%20more%20diversity%2C%20just%20like%20ours.%20Ollie's%20rotating%20recipes%20gave%20her%20a%20wider%20mix%20of%20micronutrients%20and%20amino%20acids%20throughout%20the%20week%20without%20me%20needing%20to%20buy%20multiple%20flavors%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20worth%20noting%3A%20Croc%20was%20asking%20for%20her%20meals%20earlier%20than%20usual%20with%20Ollie.%20It's%20hard%20to%20know%20whether%20she%20wasn't%20staying%20full%20for%20as%20long%20or%20was%20just%20very%2C%20very%20excited%20for%20her%20next%20meal%20and%20trying%20to%20trick%20me%20into%20feeding%20her%20earlier.%20Considering%20Ollie%20tailors%20calories%20to%20your%20dog's%20weight%20and%20activity%20level%20%E2%80%94%20and%20knowing%20my%20dog's%20food-hound%20personality%20%E2%80%94%20I%20suspect%20it%20was%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ollie%20app%20made%20it%20very%20easy%20to%20adjust%20my%20subscription%20cadence%2C%20change%20meal%20selections%2C%20and%20track%20when%20the%20next%20box%20would%20be%20delivered.%20A%20major%20feature%20of%20the%20app%20is%20its%20Health%20Screenings%2C%20where%20a%20vet%20assesses%20your%20dog's%20weight%2C%20digestion%2C%20skin%20and%20coat%2C%20and%20dental%20health%20based%20on%20photos%20you%20upload.%20The%20%26quot%3Bveterinary%20scientist%26quot%3B%20who%20is%20a%20veterinary%20technician%20either%20gives%20a%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Good%26quot%3B%20thumbs-up%20or%20offers%20basic%20recommendations%20for%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20series%20of%20screenshots%20from%20the%20Ollie%20Health%20app%20and%20email%20showing%20a%20%26quot%3BNeeds%20Improvement%26quot%3B%20skin%20and%20coat%20screening%20result%20for%20a%20dog%20named%20Croc%2C%20with%20veterinary%20recommendations%20for%20addressing%20dryness%2C%20redness%2C%20and%20mild%20hair%20loss.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f4ee5cfc04e97619b7c94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOllie%20offers%20several%20different%20health%20screenings%20within%20its%20app.%20If%20your%20screening%20shows%20a%20need%20for%20improvement%2C%20Ollie%20sends%20a%20follow-up%20email%20with%20health%20advice.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20didn't%20find%20this%20to%20be%20super%20helpful.%20For%20example%2C%20Croc's%20weight%20and%20stool%20were%20fine%2C%20as%20I%20already%20knew%2C%20but%20her%20skin%20and%20screening%20flagged%20some%20dryness%20and%20flakiness.%20The%20veterinary%20scientist%20suggested%20an%20oatmeal%20bath%20and%20omega-3%20and%20-6%20supplements%2C%20which%20makes%20sense%2C%20but%20left%20me%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20unanswered%20questions%3A%20What%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-fish-oils-for-dogs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20fish%20oil%20for%20dogs%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Could%20her%20regular%20food%20be%20the%20cause%3F%20Is%20there%20an%20oatmeal%20conditioner%2C%20or%20am%20I%20rubbing%20her%20down%20with%20breakfast%20oats%3F%20Although%20the%20advice%20came%20from%20a%20real%20vet%2C%20the%20app%20doesn't%20let%20you%20ask%20follow-up%20questions%2C%20which%20limits%20its%20usefulness.%20Ultimately%2C%20a%20photo%20analysis%20can%20only%20tell%20you%20so%20much%2C%20and%20your%20primary%20vet%20should%20always%20be%20the%20one%20to%20evaluate%20your%20dog's%20health%20and%20make%20recommendations%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229de5538b-9f9e-413f-b984-59eeae1e8357%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20minimum%20two-week%20delivery%20frequency%2C%20Ollie's%20frozen%20fresh%20food%20takes%20up%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20freezer%20space%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20standard%20top-door%20freezer%20(about%2024%20by%2014%20by%2018%20inches)%20for%20a%20medium-sized%20dog's%20meals.%20In%20a%20household%20like%20mine%20with%20an%20always-packed%20freezer%2C%20this%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20contend%20with%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20nice%20that%2095%25%20of%20the%20shipping%20packaging%20is%20recyclable%2C%20the%20individual%20food%20packs%20are%20single-use%20plastic.%20Since%20my%20dog%20eats%20an%20entire%20pack%20per%20meal%2C%20I%20was%20throwing%20out%20two%20plastic%20containers%20per%20day.%20Day%20after%20day%2C%20this%20felt%20really%20wasteful%20and%20was%20a%20huge%20con%20for%20our%20low-plastic%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20smaller%20issue%20is%20that%20the%20paddle%20was%20a%20letdown.%20It's%20decent%20for%20vertically%20chopping%20the%20food%20block%20into%20smaller%20pieces%2C%20but%20its%20spoon-like%20curved%20shape%20makes%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20scrape%20remnants%20of%20the%20packaging%20into%20the%20bowl.%20I%20always%20needed%20a%20finger%20or%20a%20different%20utensil%20to%20get%20the%20last%20bits%20off.%20After%20a%20few%20days%2C%20I%20gave%20up%20and%20just%20used%20a%20regular%20spoon.%20It%20also%20would've%20made%20more%20sense%20if%20the%20paddle%20could%20attach%20to%20the%20Ollie%20container%2C%20either%20a%20groove%20on%20the%20lid%20or%20a%20space%20inside%20to%20store%20it%20with%20the%20food%20bricks.%20Instead%2C%20it%20lived%20separately%20in%20a%20drawer%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20like%20an%20afterthought%20I%20didn't%20actually%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20con%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20Ollie%20is%20downright%20expensive.%20The%20cost%20depends%20on%20your%20dog's%20specific%20caloric%20needs%2C%20and%20the%20full%20Fresh%20plan%20starts%20at%20%241.80%20per%20meal%20for%20a%20small%20dog%2C%20which%20is%20pricier%20than%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-fresh-dog-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20fresh%20dog%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20my%2060-pound%20active%20dog%2C%20a%2028-day%20supply%20of%20Ollie's%20Fresh%20Food%20came%20out%20to%20%2473.33%20a%20week%20or%20%24293.32%20a%20month.%20The%20average%20person%20cannot%20spend%20nearly%20%24300%20a%20month%20on%20dog%20food.%20Ollie%20does%20offer%20a%20half-fresh%20plan%20for%20%2441.30%20a%20week%20for%20Croc's%20caloric%20needs%2C%20which%20I%20could%20then%20cut%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-budget-friendly-dog-foods%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20affordable%20dog%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that's%20still%20%24165.20%20a%20month%20for%20just%20half%20her%20calories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22033f9a1e-df08-4410-92a4-2daf8151ba75%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOllie%20offers%20a%20well-designed%20subscription%20service%20that%20delivers%20high-quality%2C%20stink-free%2C%20well-frozen%20fresh%20dog%20food%20delivered%20right%20to%20your%20door.%20Though%20the%20food%20bricks%20do%20take%20up%20a%20bit%20of%20freezer%20space%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20store%20and%20serve%2C%20and%20my%20dog%20went%20wild%20for%20every%20recipe.%20I%20appreciated%20that%20I%20could%20choose%20up%20to%20four%20formulas%20to%20give%20her%20a%20range%20of%20nutrients%20and%20proteins.%20While%20Ollie%2C%20like%20all%20fresh%20dog%20foods%2C%20is%20a%20bit%20expensive%20for%20the%20average%20person%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20good%20value%20for%20dogs%20who%20are%20picky%20eaters%20or%20people%20who%20want%20to%20introduce%20more%20variety%20in%20their%20dog's%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid