ed%20the%20remarkable%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithin%20a%20month%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20fill%20at%20least%2025%20large%20tin%20containers%20with%20honey%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Jagpal.%20%E2%80%9CUntil%20then%2C%20we%20had%20only%20seen%20honey%20in%20small%20bottles.%20Even%20my%20father%20was%20astonished%20and%20asked%20how%20much%20it%20could%20sell%20for.%20I%20told%20him%20each%20container%20was%20worth%20Rs%202%2C000.%20That%20was%20more%20than%20we%20could%20earn%20from%20six%20months%20of%20hard%20work%20on%20the%20wheat%20farm.%20Surprised%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20start%20this%20sooner%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jaspal%20inspecting%20a%20bee%20frame%20near%20an%20open%20beehive%20box%2C%20surrounded%20by%20multiple%20beehive%20boxes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388206%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202007%2C%20Jagpal%20quit%20teaching%20to%20devote%20himself%20fully%20to%20beekeeping.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20