ting%20hydropower%20plants%20also%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20new%20transmission%20infrastructure.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20potential%20is%20already%20being%20tapped%20in%20different%20corners%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20mines%20to%20megawatts%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20push%20to%20scale%20floating%20solar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20state-run%20power%20giant%2C%20the%20NTPC%2C%20has%20commissioned%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F118786%2Findias-largest-floating-solar-plant-in-kerala-is-now-all-set-for-operations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efloating%20solar%20projects%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Telangana%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20several%20more%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Sanjeev%20has%20been%20closely%20involved.%20%E2%80%9CChhattisgarh%20is%20blessed%20with%20numerous%20water%20bodies%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20ideal%20for%20FPV%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20state%E2%80%99s%20first%20major%20project%2C%20a%2015%20MW%20floating%20solar%20plant%2C%20is%20being%20set%20up%20by%20Steel%20Authority%20of%20India%20Limited%20(SAIL)%E2%80%93Bhilai%20at%20the%20Maroda-1%20reservoir%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20NTPC.%20It%20will%20generate%20about%2034.26%20million%20units%20annually%20for%20captive%20use%20at%20the%20Bhilai%20Steel%20Plant%2C%20helping%20reduce%20its%20carbon%20footprint.%E2%80%9D%20(In%20practice%2C%20this%20means%20the%20plant%20directly%20uses%20the%20generated%20solar%20power%2C%20reducing%20its%20need%20to%20draw%20electricity%20from%20coal-heavy%20state%20grids.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjeev%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20Maroda-1%2C%20NTPC%20has%20projects%20planned%20in%20Korba%20and%20other%20locations.%20We%20have%20mapped%20around%203%2C000%20MW%20of%20FPV%20potential%20across%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20water%20bodies%2C%20including%20a%20single%20site%2C%20Sikassa%20Dam%2C%20with%20a%20staggering%202%2C500%20MW%20potential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20FPV%20sites%20are%20traditional%20reservoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20Oriana%20Power%20commissioned%20a%201%20MWp%20floating%20solar%20plant%20for%20Udaipur%20Cement%20Works%20Limited%2C%20not%20on%20a%20river%20or%20lake%2C%20but%20on%20the%20Dabok%20mine%20pond%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deep%20water-filled%20crater%20left%20by%20years%20of%20limestone%20extraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sanjeev%20Jain%20and%20Harsh%20Tiwari%20have%20been%20working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20space%20for%20decades.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487109%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESanjeev%20Jain%20and%20Harsh%20Tiwari%20have%20been%20working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20space%20for%20decades.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20speak%20for%20themselves%3A%201.7%20million%20units%20of%20clean%20electricity%20generated%20annually%2C%204.4%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20saved%2C%20and%20evaporation%20reduced%20by%20up%20to%2070%20percent.%20That%20amount%20of%20power%20could%20meet%20the%20annual%20needs%20of%20over%20a%20thousand%20average%20Indian%20homes%2C%20while%20the%20water%20saved%20is%20nearly%20equivalent%20to%20two%20Olympic-size%20swimming%20pools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%E2%80%99s%20mining%20belts%20in%20Udaipur%2C%20Chittorgarh%2C%20and%20Nagaur%20are%20dotted%20with%20hundreds%20of%20such%20pits%2C%20now%20filled%20with%20rainwater%20or%20groundwater%20seepage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20sees%20untapped%20opportunity%20here%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20marble%20and%20stone%20mining%20areas%2C%20water%20used%20for%20cutting%20is%20collected%20in%20large%20ponds%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20seep%20much%20because%20of%20the%20stone%20bed.%20These%20ponds%20could%20host%20FPV%20to%20power%20nearby%20industrial%20zones%20or%20feed%20backup%20power%20to%20the%20grid.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20productive%20reuse%20of%20land%20and%20water%2C%20plus%20renewable%20generation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20beyond%20powering%20industries%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20floating%20solar%20reaches%20well%20past%20the%20energy%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20promise%20beyond%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20an%20engineering%20win%2C%20floating%20solar%20is%20an%20environmental%20ally%2C%20whose%20benefits%20go%20beyond%20power%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335435%2Fiit-guwahati-startup-quant-solar-technologies-floating-solar-plant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWater%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Panels%20block%20sunlight%2C%20cutting%20evaporation%20losses%20by%20up%20to%2090%20percent%20and%20suppressing%20algae%20growth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECarbon%20savings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20FPV%20on%20hydropower%20reservoirs%20could%20cut%203.3%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20annually.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20deployment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20No%20major%20earthworks%20are%20needed%2C%20avoiding%20the%20cost%20and%20disruption%20of%20site%20preparation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20advantages%2C%20the%20question%20is%20how%20widely%20this%20technology%20can%20be%20deployed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20answer%20could%20be%20game-changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGigawatts%20waiting%20to%20be%20tapped%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20India%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20backwaters%20to%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20mine%20ponds%20%E2%80%94%20FPV%20is%20gathering%20momentum.%20Experts%20say%20the%20theoretical%20potential%20exceeds%20200%20gigawatts%20(GW)%20if%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20reservoirs%20hosted%20floating%20solar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-3-1755164208.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FPV%20frees%20up%20land%20for%20agriculture%2C%20housing%2C%20or%20conservation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-3-1755164208.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-3-1755164208-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-3-1755164208-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-3-1755164208-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-s