lour%20and%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExperimentation%20and%20a%20quest%20for%20quality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20growing%20the%20flowers%20presented%20their%20own%20set%20of%20challenges.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20obstructions%20Lohith%20faced%20was%20the%20flower%E2%80%99s%20light%20sensitivity.%20%E2%80%9CChrysanthemum%20is%20a%20light-sensitive%20crop.%20It%20requires%2017-18%20hours%20of%20darkness%2C%20which%20is%20only%20possible%20during%20winter.%20Managing%20this%20in%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20longer%20summer%20days%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20He%20also%20found%20that%20chrysanthemums%20grown%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20performed%20differently%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20experiment%20with%20various%20varieties%20like%20pink%20Santini%2C%20yellow%20Santini%2C%20and%20red%20calimero%20to%20find%20the%20best%20fit%20for%20the%20local%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202483px)%20100vw%2C%202483px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222483%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lohith%20sells%20his%20chrysanthemums%20to%20wholesalers%20and%20event%20managers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878.jpg%202483w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878-1536x1152